Create TODO List in Angular using Different Components 
Step 1 — Install Angular CLI 
Open terminal and install Angular CLI globally. 
npm install -g @angular/cli Check installation: 
	ng version 
 
Step 2 — Create Angular Project Create a new Angular project. 
	ng new todo-app 
Select the following options: Stylesheet format → CSS 
Server Side Rendering → No AI Tools → None 
Move into the project folder: 
	cd todo-app 
 
Step 3 — Run Angular Project Start Angular development server. 
	ng serve Open browser: 
http://localhost:4200 Default Angular page will appear. 
 
Step 4 — Generate TODO Component Create a new component named todo.  
	ng generate component todo Angular creates the following files: 
src/app/todo 
   todo.ts    todo.html    todo.css 
   todo.spec.ts 
 
Step 5 — Edit App Component Open: 
src/app/app.ts update code with the following: import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Todo } from './todo/todo'; 
@Component({ 
  selector: 'app-root',   imports: [Todo],   templateUrl: './app.html',   styleUrl: './app.css' 
}) 
export class App { } 
 
Step 6 — Edit App HTML Open: 
src/app/app.html Delete everything and add: 
<app-todo></app-todo> 
 
Step 7 — Write Todo Component Code Open: 
src/app/todo/todo.ts Update the code with: import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { FormsModule } from '@angular/forms'; 
import { CommonModule } from '@angular/common'; 
 
@Component({ 
  selector: 'app-todo', 
  standalone: true,   imports: [FormsModule, CommonModule], 
  templateUrl: './todo.html', 
  styleUrl: './todo.css' 
}) 
 
export class Todo {   task = '';   todos: string[] = []; 
 
  addTodo() {     if (this.task.trim()) {       this.todos.push(this.task);       this.task = ''; 
    } 
  } 
  deleteTodo(index: number) {     this.todos.splice(index, 1); 
  } 
 
} 
  
  
Step 8 — Write Todo HTML Open: src/app/todo/todo.html Delete all existing code and add: 
<h2>My Todos</h2> 
 
<input [(ngModel)]="task" placeholder="What needs to be done?"> 
<button (click)="addTodo()">Add</button> 
 
<ul> 
  <li *ngFor="let todo of todos; let i = index"> 
    {{ todo }} 
    <button (click)="deleteTodo(i)">Delete</button> 
  </li> 
</ul> 
 
Step 9 — Run the Application Run the project again. 
 ng serve Open browser: 
http://localhost:4200 
   
   
   
    
   
   
   
